### Ingest image with multipart/form-data
POST http://localhost:3000/api/ingest/image
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=TurnUpBoundary

--TurnUpBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="userId"

demo-user
--TurnUpBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="flyer.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./fixtures/flyer.jpg
--TurnUpBoundary--

### Ingest image with base64 JSON
POST http://localhost:3000/api/ingest/image
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "demo-user",
  "mimeType": "image/png",
  "base64Image": "iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAA..."
}

### Ingest social link
POST http://localhost:3000/api/ingest/link
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "demo-user",
  "url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/EXAMPLE/"
}

### Get profile data
GET http://localhost:3000/api/profile?userId=demo-user

### Add stash item manually
POST http://localhost:3000/api/profile/stash
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "demo-user",
  "itemType": "link",
  "title": "uab.ca/scholarships",
  "subtitle": "Bookmarked Apr 12",
  "detailLabel": "Saved link",
  "sourceUrl": "https://www.ualberta.ca/"
}

### Regenerate insights
POST http://localhost:3000/api/profile/insights/regenerate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "demo-user"
}
